Sir,

302
00:25:57,740 --> 00:25:58,300
I'm busy.

303
00:25:58,630 --> 00:25:59,400
I'm not buying.

304
00:26:01,300 --> 00:26:02,020
I'm a cop.

305
00:26:17,670 --> 00:26:18,170
You... -I...

306
00:26:20,460 --> 00:26:21,130
You go first.

307
00:26:22,060 --> 00:26:22,510
No need.

308
00:26:22,770 --> 00:26:23,940
It's okay. You go first.

309
00:26:24,010 --> 00:26:24,750
I'm fine.

310
