312
00:26:30,890 --> 00:26:31,590
I don't know him.

313
00:26:31,620 --> 00:26:32,480
Is he under the bridge?

314
00:26:32,500 --> 00:26:32,900
Yes.

315
00:26:45,410 --> 00:26:46,560
Since this is the police station,

316
00:26:47,050 --> 00:26:47,840
I want to report a case.

317
00:26:48,580 --> 00:26:49,280
Tell me.

318
00:26:50,210 --> 00:26:51,060
There's a man.

319
00:26:52,380 --> 00:26:53,660
