320
00:26:54,120 --> 00:26:54,690
He had

321
00:26:54,690 --> 00:26:55,600
an unknown accident.

322
00:26:55,890 --> 00:26:57,070
He's lying in the grass below.

323
00:26:57,600 --> 00:26:58,140
Anyway,

324
00:26:58,670 --> 00:26:59,660
he's in a bad condition.

325
00:27:00,190 --> 00:27:01,400
Go and help him.

326
00:27:03,680 --> 00:27:04,770
So you're here to turn yourself in?

327
00:27:04,920 --> 00:27:06,390
