328
00:27:06,410 --> 00:27:07,440
You just said it was bad.

329
00:27:07,680 --> 00:27:08,370
What is it?

330
00:27:09,010 --> 00:27:09,770
His body

331
00:27:10,660 --> 00:27:11,540
is broken like

332
00:27:11,570 --> 00:27:12,440
puzzle pieces.

333
00:27:14,220 --> 00:27:15,150
What did you just say? Turn yourself in?

334
00:27:15,190 --> 00:27:15,990
I'm here to report a case.

335
00:27:16,050 --> 00:27:17,440
Think about what you just said.

336
00:27:17,530 --> 00:27:19,190
