337
00:27:20,030 --> 00:27:20,620
This person...

338
00:27:20,660 --> 00:27:21,290
This thing...

339
00:27:21,310 --> 00:27:22,010
Say it quickly.

340
00:27:27,200 --> 00:27:28,520
