365
00:28:08,920 --> 00:28:09,920
Why did you translate it like this?

366
00:28:10,590 --> 00:28:11,530
I was not lying.

367
00:28:11,970 --> 00:28:13,010
You can see it yourself. -I've been there.

368
00:28:13,070 --> 00:28:13,800
There's nothing.

369
00:28:14,160 --> 00:28:15,300
Where did you hide him?

370
00:28:15,360 --> 00:28:16,110
I didn't.

371
00:28:19,500 --> 00:28:20,140
He's gone?

372
00:28:27,160 --> 00:28:28,850
Yes, there was no body.

373
00:28:29,670 --> 00:28:31,010
In this case, we can't even confirm

374
00:28:31,040 --> 00:28:31,750
what he is suspicious of.

375
00:28:34,850 --> 00:28:36,650
Yes, there's no body.

376
00:28:37,740 --> 00:28:39,030
Am I a bigger suspect?

377
00:28:39,990 --> 00:28:40,560
What should I do?

378
00:28:43,520 --> 00:28:44,320
The director is coming.

379
00:28:44,740 --> 00:28:45,440
If he finds out I'm doing this to a civilian

380
00:28:45,460 --> 00:28:46,740
in the middle of the night, I'm dead.

381
00:28:47,680 --> 00:28:48,770
Why is she checking the time?

382
00:28:49,920 --> 00:28:50,940
She must be impatient.

383
00:28:51,660 --> 00:28:52,900
What will she do to me?

384
00:28:58,400 --> 00:28:59,350
Name, phone number, and address.

385
00:28:59,680 --> 00:29:00,870
I'll sue you for forgery documents, if you make things up.

386
00:29:21,120 --> 00:29:21,750
Go back first.

387
00:29:22,250 --> 00:29:22,890
I'll call you again.

388
00:29:42,910 --> 00:29:43,480
Are you going to work?

389
00:29:44,650 --> 00:29:45,150
Weren't you...

390
00:29:46,660 --> 00:29:47,500
Where did you go?

391
00:29:48,170 --> 00:29:48,680
I went running.

392
00:29:49,360 --> 00:29:50,110
Wearing a coat?

393
00:29:50,460 --> 00:29:51,400
Then I don't need to warm up.

394
00:29:51,430 --> 00:29:52,570
What are you talking about?

395
00:30:24,320 --> 00:30:24,780
Keep moving.

396
00:30:25,100 --> 00:30:25,670
He's upstairs.

397
00:30:48,730 --> 00:30:49,810
[Night Freak]

398
00:30:55,310 --> 00:30:55,970
Zheng Lisong.

399
00:30:58,190 --> 00:30:59,060
Mr. Zheng Lisong?

400
00:31:00,400 --> 00:31:00,860
Probably.

401
00:31:01,000 --> 00:31:01,580
I didn't ask you.

402
00:31:02,490 --> 00:31:03,550
Can you stand up?

403
00:32:01,510 --> 00:32:02,060
Help me.

404
00:32:07,920 --> 00:32:08,460
Police!

405
00:32:15,670 --> 00:32:16,320
Hit the police!

406
00:32:18,590 --> 00:32:19,330
Help me!

407
00:32:22,010 --> 00:32:22,730
What is it?

408
00:32:25,560 --> 00:32:27,170
I told you, but you didn't believe me.

409
00:32:29,850 --> 00:32:30,760
Don't come any closer.

410
00:32:32,000 --> 00:32:33,050
If you come any closer, I'm going to kill him!

411
00:32:38,200 --> 00:32:39,000
Who is this?

412
00:32:47,660 --> 00:32:49,570
Although your face is rotten like this, I can still see it's you.

413
00:32:49,590 --> 00:32:50,100
No.

414
00:32:56,000 --> 00:32:56,670
It's you.

415
00:32:57,100 --> 00:32:57,800
Not me.

416
00:32:58,660 --> 00:32:59,390
It's you.

417
00:32:59,840 --> 00:33:00,480
Not me.

418
00:33:01,170 --> 00:33:01,880
It's you.

419
00:33:02,010 --> 00:33:02,790
Not me.

420
00:33:03,580 --> 00:33:04,260
Forget it.

421
00:33:04,830 --> 00:33:05,840
Let me introduce.

422
00:33:06,080 --> 00:33:06,520
This is

423
00:33:07,030 --> 00:33:07,650
Chen Chuying,

424
00:33:07,800 --> 00:33:08,350
a police officer.

425
00:33:08,660 --> 00:33:09,770
This must be the victim.

426
00:33:10,720 --> 00:33:11,020
Okay.

427
00:33:11,220 --> 00:33:12,020
You can leave now.

428
00:33:16,460 --> 00:33:17,740
Aren't you looking for help?

429
00:33:18,010 --> 00:33:18,670
Although she doesn't look like one,

430
00:33:19,110 --> 00:33:20,430
she is really a police officer.

431
00:33:20,740 --> 00:33:21,830
Let's go. I'll walk you out.

432
00:33:22,040 --> 00:33:22,670
No. -No!

433
00:33:23,010 --> 00:33:23,770
Why not?

434
00:33:23,890 --> 00:33:24,970
Because he... -I'm not asking you.

435
00:33:27,350 --> 00:33:28,080
I don't know.

436
00:33:28,710 --> 00:33:29,390
Why again?

437
00:33:30,080 --> 00:33:31,100
What do you know?

438
00:33:32,500 --> 00:33:33,830
I know I'm not that person

439
00:33:33,850 --> 00:33:35,080
and I won't leave you.

440
00:33:43,650 --> 00:33:44,460
I want to report a case to you.

441
00:33:45,500 --> 00:33:46,250
I can't accept it now.

442
00:33:53,540 --> 00:33:55,190
It can't be seen.

443
00:33:56,510 --> 00:33:59,080
Don't let them find my body.

444
00:34:39,469 --> 00:34:40,850
You mean that dead man?

445
00:34:40,880 --> 00:34:42,739
Please wear his body and walk around.

446
00:34:43,889 --> 00:34:44,630
Who are you?

447
00:34:47,199 --> 00:34:47,699
Kappa!

448
00:34:48,260 --> 00:34:49,810
I'm a kappa!

449
00:34:50,699 --> 00:34:51,719
I don't care what you are.

450
00:34:52,010 --> 00:34:53,139
Give the body back to the deceased.

451
00:34:53,520 --> 00:34:54,270
He has a family.

452
00:34:54,760 --> 00:34:55,370
I can't.

453
00:34:55,760 --> 00:34:56,270
Why?

454
00:35:01,200 --> 00:35:02,410
The strength of human heart

455
00:35:03,650 --> 00:35:05,820
is much stronger than skin, bones and flesh.

456
00:35:07,570 --> 00:35:08,680
That's why I can't.

457
00:35:11,210 --> 00:35:13,050
Luckily, I have this body,

458
00:35:15,370 --> 00:35:16,600
so I can come to you.

459
00:35:17,500 --> 00:35:18,930
So what do you want from me?

460
00:35:19,360 --> 00:35:19,950
Help me.

461
00:35:20,350 --> 00:35:20,860
With what?

462
00:35:20,990 --> 00:35:21,660
I don't know.

463
00:35:22,210 --> 00:35:22,710
Again?

464
00:35:27,810 --> 00:35:28,920
This motorbike is registered

465
00:35:28,950 --> 00:35:30,710
under Zheng Lisong, a 34-year-old man.

466
00:35:31,130 --> 00:35:33,090
There are signs of high-speed collision in the lower half of the guardrail.

467
00:35:33,560 --> 00:35:35,570
There's a piece of scalp tissue on the bike lane.

468
00:35:35,850 --> 00:35:37,660
After the collision, the rider fell off the bridge.

469
00:35:38,470 --> 00:35:39,770
But the rider who should have died

470
00:35:39,810 --> 00:35:40,780
is missing.

471
00:35:42,080 --> 00:35:42,990
We've compared.

472
00:35:43,450 --> 00:35:46,280
The blood and tissue are consistent with the owner Zheng Lisong.

473
00:35:46,810 --> 00:35:47,860
He had no criminal record.

474
00:35:48,980 --> 00:35:50,000
He lived with his parents.

475
00:35:50,130 --> 00:35:51,010
He had no siblings.

476
00:35:51,520 --> 00:35:53,240
He entered the medical center a year ago.

477
00:35:53,500 --> 00:35:54,660
First, he was a clinical pharmacist.

478
00:35:54,690 --> 00:35:55,660
Then he became a pharmacist.

479
00:35:56,190 --> 00:35:57,750
His colleagues said they were not familiar with him.

480
00:35:58,950 --> 00:35:59,910
Do you have any questions?

481
00:36:00,280 --> 00:36:00,790
One-per.

482
00:36:02,150 --> 00:36:02,730
One-per.

483
00:36:04,270 --> 00:36:05,170
Excuse me.

484
00:36:05,520 --> 00:36:06,780
Let me see who's so rude

485
00:36:06,810 --> 00:36:07,930
to call your team leader One-per?

486
00:36:10,480 --> 00:36:11,140
One-per.

487
00:36:14,510 --> 00:36:16,270
When your director told me,

488
00:36:16,400 --> 00:36:17,660
I only believed 80% of it.

489
00:36:18,320 --> 00:36:20,550
But you've really been wandering around all day long.

490
00:36:20,890 --> 00:36:21,640
Where did you go?

491
00:36:22,860 --> 00:36:23,800
Senior, please continue.

492
00:36:26,320 --> 00:36:27,350
First, it's a small matter.

493
00:36:28,280 --> 00:36:28,950
We suspected

494
00:36:28,970 --> 00:36:30,840
if he had a sudden relapse

495
00:36:30,860 --> 00:36:31,800
that caused the accident?

496
00:36:32,420 --> 00:36:34,170
Based on his medical record,

497
00:36:34,200 --> 00:36:35,470
he's basically healthy.

498
00:36:35,810 --> 00:36:36,660
But he had high blood pressure.

499
00:36:37,130 --> 00:36:38,250
Even his parents didn't know.

500
00:36:38,470 --> 00:36:39,970
And they didn't believe it.

501
00:36:41,250 --> 00:36:43,140
A 34-year-old with high blood pressure, was he born with it?

502
00:36:44,230 --> 00:36:44,810
No.

503
00:36:46,340 --> 00:36:47,790
But he's been going to the doctor and taking medicine.

504
00:36:47,890 --> 00:36:48,750
It's not a problem.

505
00:36:49,080 --> 00:36:50,180
That's why I said it's a small matter.

506
00:36:52,060 --> 00:36:53,070
But there's another point.

507
00:36:53,890 --> 00:36:54,470
He has insurances.

508
00:36:55,180 --> 00:36:56,360
And he insured with a few companies.

509
00:36:56,790 --> 00:36:57,790
They are all high compensation insurances.

510
00:37:02,900 --> 00:37:04,570
You were there at the accident scene.

511
00:37:05,490 --> 00:37:06,700
You also checked the motorbike.

512
00:37:08,990 --> 00:37:10,540
There was no trace of hit-and-run by another vehicle.

513
00:37:12,850 --> 00:37:14,620
Judging from the amount of bleeding,

514
00:37:14,640 --> 00:37:16,200
there is a high probability that

515
00:37:16,230 --> 00:37:17,770
the insurance company will judge death.

516
00:37:19,260 --> 00:37:20,410
But he studied medicine.

517
00:37:21,060 --> 00:37:22,420
So we... -Did he fake his death?

518
00:37:28,590 --> 00:37:29,650
Fake death?

519
00:37:35,720 --> 00:37:37,010
Can he do that?

520
00:37:38,160 --> 00:37:38,780
Impossible.

521
00:37:40,110 --> 00:37:40,780
Senior, let me ask you.

522
00:37:41,020 --> 00:37:41,830
If you die...

523
00:37:45,750 --> 00:37:46,310
One more time.

524
00:37:46,350 --> 00:37:47,630
Why did you knock four times?

525
00:37:47,960 --> 00:37:49,220
The last one is on the house. Whatever.

526
00:37:49,630 --> 00:37:50,260
I wanted to ask you.

527
00:37:50,460 --> 00:37:51,420
If you die,

528
00:37:51,550 --> 00:37:53,170
and you don't want your body to be seen,

529
00:37:54,030 --> 00:37:54,460
Why?

530
00:37:59,180 --> 00:38:00,090
If I die,

531
00:38:02,030 --> 00:38:03,000
I would still be handsome.

532
00:38:03,460 --> 00:38:04,960
I'll just let others find me and watch.

533
00:38:05,430 --> 00:38:06,230
I don't care.

534
00:38:07,190 --> 00:38:08,700
But others might not think so.

535
00:38:09,700 --> 00:38:11,480
Didn't our team handle

536
00:38:11,640 --> 00:38:13,140
a motel case before?

537
00:38:13,610 --> 00:38:15,560
It made us blush.

538
00:38:16,100 --> 00:38:16,690
If I were him,

539
00:38:16,870 --> 00:38:18,350
I wouldn't let others see me die like that.

540
00:38:23,370 --> 00:38:24,450
Why do you know so much?

541
00:38:25,720 --> 00:38:27,770
If you want to transfer to the Investigation Team, take the exam.

542
00:38:31,990 --> 00:38:32,900
I forgot.

543
00:38:33,650 --> 00:38:34,620
You're One-per.

544
00:38:37,830 --> 00:38:38,310
Come on.

545
00:38:40,030 --> 00:38:42,710
One-per. Good luck in the exam. -Go to hell, Cui Zhaowan!

546
00:38:41,890 --> 00:38:43,010
[Investigation Team]

547
00:38:42,740 --> 00:38:43,540
Who would get promoted

548
00:38:43,570 --> 00:38:44,540
with a lame exam?

549
00:38:44,680 --> 00:38:45,720
It's even more awesome to get a reward for solving cases.

550
00:38:46,000 --> 00:38:47,240
So Cui Zhaowan, die!

551
00:38:55,310 --> 00:38:55,800
Lie in here.

552
00:38:57,560 --> 00:38:58,200
Again?

553
00:38:58,940 --> 00:38:59,990
I'm not lying this time.

554
00:39:00,700 --> 00:39:01,460
Hide here.

555
00:39:01,680 --> 00:39:02,670
Let me check if they'll find out.

556
00:39:04,100 --> 00:39:05,410
And it wasn't a lie last time.

557
00:39:22,260 --> 00:39:23,500
You can't go down.

558
00:39:24,190 --> 00:39:25,540
My mom won't come up either.

559
00:39:26,380 --> 00:39:27,310
Even if she finds out,

560
00:39:27,340 --> 00:39:28,800
you look better in this.

561
00:39:36,200 --> 00:39:36,770
Does it hurt?

562
00:39:40,040 --> 00:39:40,620
Not you.

563
00:39:41,070 --> 00:39:41,760
The owner of your body.

564
00:39:42,810 --> 00:39:44,050
When he was hit,

565
00:39:44,710 --> 00:39:45,890
