566
00:39:46,640 --> 00:39:47,360
Would you know?

567
00:39:51,370 --> 00:39:52,120
No.

568
00:40:03,550 --> 00:40:04,490
You made an appointment with me?

569
00:40:05,430 --> 00:40:06,060
How is that possible?

570
00:40:12,680 --> 00:40:13,010
Mom.

571
00:40:14,230 --> 00:40:15,870
Do you have any photos or videos from that time?

572
00:40:17,280 --> 00:40:18,480
Not the ones from the news.

573
00:40:19,730 --> 00:40:20,910
Photos of the people

574
00:40:23,780 --> 00:40:24,620
